3 Termination
-----------------

3.1 The permissions granted under this License will terminate automatically
    if You fail to comply with any of its Terms and Conditions. However, if You become
    compliant, then the permissions granted under this License are reinstated.
     
3.2 If you were notified that your permissions are revoked, the permissions granted
    by this license can only be reinstated to you manually by the copyright holder.
     
3.3 If you were banned from the repository, it means that permissions granted to You by 
    this License are terminated and cannot be reinstated until the ban is lifted.

3.4 If you dont have the permissions granted under Section 2.2.2, you must remove 
    any material covered by this License from your posession. This includes 
    but not limited to forks, code, local checkouts and Compiled Binaries.
     
